Today we’re continuing with part 2 of Tommy Robinson: Silenced. As the story unfolds, we go deeper into the forces at play — the media, the state, the public reaction — and ask what it reveals about our ability to have open, honest conversations in an increasingly polarised world. This isn’t just about one person — it’s about the bigger picture: power, truth, and whether we’re still able to hear each other at all. Watch with us.
